thread.title: Indian Overseas Bank Dec Qtr Loss Widens

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Indian Overseas Bank Dec Qtr Loss Widens
text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - Indian Overseas Bank:
* DEC QUARTER NET LOSS 9.71 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS LOSS OF 5.54 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 42.55 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 48.81 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS AND CONTINGENCIES 16.40 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 14.06 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 21.95 PERCENT VERSUS 22.73 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 13.08 PERCENT VERSUS 13.86 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text - bit.ly/2Ez1L3J Further company coverage:
